OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782294489
OL,3,CSchools announce early closures to
OL,4,Cprotect pupils in extreme heat
OL,6,FSome schools have announced early
OL,7,Fclosures while others have asked
OL,8,Fparents to pick up their children
OL,9,Fbefore the end of the normal day where
OL,10,Fpossible in an effort to protect
OL,11,Fpupils amid extreme heat this week.
OL,13,FIt comes as forecasters say
OL,14,Ftemperatures could soar to 38C to 40C
OL,15,Fin some parts of England and Wales
OL,16,Fduring the heatwave.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
