OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782294489
OL,3,CSchools announce early closures to
OL,4,Cprotect pupils in extreme heat
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency has
OL,7,Fissued a red health warning for six
OL,8,Fregions of England from 1am on
OL,9,FWednesday until 11pm on Thursday.
OL,10,FAffected areas include Bath, Somerset,
OL,11,FBristol, Dorset, Gloucestershire,
OL,12,FSwindon and Wiltshire.
OL,14,FNumerous schools in the region have
OL,15,Fannounced early closures. Kingdown
OL,16,FSchool and The Clarendon Academy, both
OL,17,Fin Wiltshire, will close at 12.25pm
OL,18,Ffrom Monday to Thursday.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782294489
OL,3,CSchools announce early closures to
OL,4,Cprotect pupils in extreme heat
OL,6,FCirencester Deer Park Secondary in
OL,7,FGloucestershire will also close just
OL,8,Fafter midday.
OL,10,F"We have been closely monitoring the
OL,11,Fweather forecast for the coming week,
OL,12,Fwith temperatures expected to exceed
OL,13,F34C from Monday June 22 to Thursday
OL,14,FJune 25," Kingdown School said on its
OL,15,Fwebsite.
OL,17,F"To prioritise the safety and
OL,18,Fwellbeing of our students and staff,
OL,19,Fwe have made the decision to implement
OL,20,Fan early finish on these days."
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@IO]yD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
