CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1782294489
OL,3,CSchools announce early closures to
OL,4,Cprotect pupils in extreme heat
OL,6,FThe Met Office said people can also
OL,7,Fexpect travel disruptions, including
OL,8,Fdelays on roads and road closures as
OL,9,Fwell as delays and cancellations to
OL,10,Frail and air travel.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
